item.title: Projects
item.dc:creator: liz
item.content:encoded: As part of a second year college group project, I was involved in the design of a website for http://www.lucysloungedesign.com, a vintage boutique which specialises in making unique items from upcycled clothes while teaching people to sew.My main responsibilites included creating website design and layout mockups in photoshop, photography for the website and interviewing people for testimonials.  Screenshots of webpages       Photography from the website
